{"id":1415,"date":"2019-01-15T16:31:31","date_gmt":"2019-01-15T09:31:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/?p=1415"},"modified":"2019-01-15T17:04:58","modified_gmt":"2019-01-15T10:04:58","slug":"hach-toan-chi-phi-xay-dung-khach-san-5-sao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/hach-toan-chi-phi-xay-dung-khach-san-5-sao","title":{"rendered":"H\u1ea1ch to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao \u0111i v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0: Chi ph\u00ed thu\u00ea \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, chi ph\u00ed duy tr\u00ec ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u00f4m nay, <strong>Thietkethicongdn.com<\/strong> xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/hach-toan-chi-phi-xay-dung-khach-san-5-sao\"><em><strong>H\u1ea1ch to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO<\/strong><\/em><\/a><\/span>. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1417 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/H\u1ea1ch-to\u00e1n-chi-ph\u00ed-x\u00e2y-d\u1ef1ng-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-5-SAO1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"307\" \/><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span id=\"Tong_quan_ve_chi_phi_hoan_thien_khach_san\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u01a1n gi\u00e1 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO giao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 5tr &#8211; 15tr\/m2. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed n\u1ed9i, ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ph\u00ed ph\u00e1t sinh kh\u00e1c th\u00ec kinh ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh tr\u00ean 1000 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng chi ph\u00ed ph\u00e1t sinh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>1. Chi ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ednh tr\u00ean di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh, m\u1ed7i m2 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eeb 200.000\u0111 tr\u1edf l\u00ean. T\u00f9y v\u00e0o di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed theo \u0111\u00f3 nh\u00e2n l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2. Chi ph\u00ed ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi ph\u00ed ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO s\u1ebd ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf. V\u00ec quy m\u00f4 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c. Chi ph\u00ed cho t\u1eebng h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed nh\u00e2n c\u00f4ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i (C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng n\u0103m) n\u00ean c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n kinh ph\u00ed v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2.1. Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u1ef9 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cao t\u1ea7ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1416 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/H\u1ea1ch-to\u00e1n-chi-ph\u00ed-x\u00e2y-d\u1ef1ng-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-5-SAO.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"336\" \/><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt; C\u00f2n ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb g\u00ec n\u1eefa m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi <strong>Milimet vu\u00f4ng (MM2) &#8211;\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/thiet-ke-thi-cong-nha-tai-da-nang\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi c\u00f4ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng<\/a><\/span><\/strong> \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam chi ti\u1ebft.<\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ean 10.000m2 b\u1edfi m\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t gi\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01a1n: 24m2<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t gi\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4i ho\u1eb7c 2 gi\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01a1n: 32m2<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eb7t bi\u1ec7t: 56m2<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng cao c\u1ea5p: 100m2<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh: Bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00f2ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c, ph\u00f2ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5, khi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3, khu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, nh\u00e0 kho, n\u01a1i gi\u1eb7t l\u00e0&#8230;<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00f2ng \u0103n<\/li>\n<li>Khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; Kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf cao t\u1ea7ng n\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 thang m\u00e1y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c t\u1ea7ng. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thanh m\u00e1y \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u00ec s\u1ebd t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n lo\u1ea1i thang m\u00e1y th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n, th\u00f4ng gi\u00f3 v\u00e0 tho\u00e1t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2.2. Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9. Kh\u00f4ng gian t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0o trong c\u1ea7n trau chu\u1ed1t nghi\u00eam ch\u1ec9nh. M\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao, ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1420 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/H\u1ea1ch-to\u00e1n-chi-ph\u00ed-x\u00e2y-d\u1ef1ng-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-5-SAO4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"375\" \/><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; XEM TH\u00caM\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/bat-mi-thiet-ke-sanh-khach-san-dep-lung-linh-va-an-tuong-nhat-2019\">[B\u1eacT M\u00cd] Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb9p lung linh v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t 2019<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> n\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2y xanh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e1t m\u1ebb. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u00eam d\u00e0i phun n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn x\u00e2y b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i ch\u00e2n m\u00e2y tr\u00e0n b\u1edd ph\u00eda tr\u00ean s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&#8211; <strong>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> th\u00ec c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1418 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/H\u1ea1ch-to\u00e1n-chi-ph\u00ed-x\u00e2y-d\u1ef1ng-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-5-SAO2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"337\" \/><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t s\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7, t\u1ea1o cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u1edf nh\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 v\u1ec7 sinh theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed, ph\u00f2ng gym, qu\u1ea7y bar c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ri\u00eang. C\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb trong ph\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch ngh\u1ec9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1419 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/H\u1ea1ch-to\u00e1n-chi-ph\u00ed-x\u00e2y-d\u1ef1ng-kh\u00e1ch-s\u1ea1n-5-SAO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"333\" \/><\/p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&gt;&gt;&gt; \u0110\u1eeaNG B\u1ece L\u1ee0\u00a0<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/7-loai-giuong-trong-khach-san-ma-ban-can-biet\">7 lo\u1ea1i gi\u01b0\u1eddng trong kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft!<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n n\u00ean c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eeb c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia trong to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao \u0111i v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0: Chi ph\u00ed thu\u00ea \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, chi ph\u00ed duy tr\u00ec ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u00f4m nay, Thietkethicongdn.com xin gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n H\u1ea1ch to\u00e1n chi ph\u00ed x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 SAO. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i nh\u00e9!&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1417,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1415"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1415"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1415\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1438,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1415\/revisions\/1438"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1417"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1415"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1415"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thietkethicongdn.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1415"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}